(g) when the landlord fails to carry out any repairs for which he is liable, to order the landlord to carry out such repairs ;
when the landlord fails to carry out any repairs for which he is liable, to order the landlord to carry out such repairs ;
(h) to permit the levy of distress for standard rent ;
